All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
AdminController
The class AdminController will provide functionality on the admin screen to the photos application
Album
The class Album will represent a photo album
Application
The class Application will provide basic functionality and maintain the user list and current application variables
InsideAlbumController
The class InsideAlbumController will provide functionality for the application when inside an a photo album
LoginController
The LoginController class will handle login functionality for the photos application
NonAdminController
The class NonAdminController will provide functionality on the non-admin screen for the photos application
Photo
The class Photo represents a photo in a photo album
Photos
The class Photos is the driver for the photos application
PhotoSlideshowController
The class PhotoSlideshowController will provide slideshow functionality for an album
SearchController
The class SearchController will provide search functionality within a photo album
Tag
The class Tag represents a tag for a photo
Thumbnail
The Thumbnail class represents a thumbnail image for a photo
User
The User class will represent a user of the application.
